Help on skill: claws storm
Skill type: offensive
Usage duration: random
Affecting stats: Dex/Str
Affecting skills: Dragon blow, Claws storm, Whirlwind

Skill claws storm is for whirling towards the target and by using his knuckles, the martial artists can
tear his target totally. This skill teaches how to control body and teaches the basics about
power focusing and how the martial artist can concentrate for combat. 
If artists doesn't know the basics of the way of being a martial artists, this skill won't be really
powerful but skilled enough can deal much damage with this skill.
